  "chapters": [
    {
      "chapter_id": "ch18",
      "text": "This chamber… it’s alive. The walls are breathing.",
      "content_image": null,
      "character": { "name": "Alex", "image": "https://ix-marketing.imgix.net/focalpoint.png" },
      "isUser": true
    },
    {
      "chapter_id": "ch19",
      "text": "Central pedestal just activated. Something wants to interface with us.",
      "content_image": null,
      "character": { "name": "Bob", "image": "https://ix-marketing.imgix.net/footer-image.png" },
      "isUser": false
    },
    {
      "chapter_id": "ch20",
      "text": "I’m seeing memories that aren’t mine—stars dying, a war older than galaxies…",
      "content_image": null,
      "character": { "name": "Alex", "image": "https://ix-marketing.imgix.net/focalpoint.png" },
      "isUser": true
    },
    {
      "chapter_id": "ch21",
      "text": "It’s the last archivist of a dead civilization. It’s been waiting millions of years… for someone to carry its warning.",
      "content_image": null,
      "character": { "name": "Bob", "image": "https://ix-marketing.imgix.net/footer-image.png" },
      "isUser": false
    },
    {
      "chapter_id": "ch22",
      "text": "Warning about what?",
      "content_image": null,
      "character": { "name": "Alex", "image": "https://ix-marketing.imgix.net/focalpoint.png" },
      "isUser": true
    },
    {
      "chapter_id": "ch23",
      "text": "Something’s coming back. The thing that killed them. And it just woke up because we tripped its beacon.",
      "content_image": null,
      "character": { "name": "Bob", "image": "https://ix-marketing.imgix.net/footer-image.png" },
      "isUser": false
    },
    {
      "chapter_id": "ch24",
      "text": "You’re saying we just rang the dinner bell for a galaxy-eating horror?",
      "content_image": null,
      "character": { "name": "Alex", "image": "https://ix-marketing.imgix.net/focalpoint.png" },
      "isUser": true
    },
    {
      "chapter_id": "ch25",
      "text": "Pretty much. The archivist is offering us the only weapon that ever hurt it… if we accept the knowledge.",
      "content_image": null,
      "character": { "name": "Bob", "image": "https://ix-marketing.imgix.net/footer-image.png" },
      "isUser": false
    }
  ],
  "choices": [
    { "text": "Accept the ancient weapon-knowledge", "next_scene": "scene4" }
  ]
